    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The process of securing the text block and attached endpapers into a case that was produced as a separate operation.  For the process of attaching individual boards to the text block and end papers, if any, use "board attachment."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
